c: 7
v: 145
t: "Ni twannembele jwalakwejo m’maubawu kuumila mu chindu chilichose chiigaanyo, ni kusalichisya kwa chindu chilichose, (ni kuntenda kuti): “Basi gakamulisyani mwamachili, ni mwalamuleje ŵandu ŵenu kuti agakamulisyeje mwaumbone wakwe wannope. Pangakaŵapa chinannosye misi ja ŵakunyosya.”"